parameters: Excuse me, is it okay if we proceed today as well?

Well, it can't be helped. We've already boarded
this ship, after all.
It's fine, but in return, please be gentle, okay?

How many times has it been since I was first asked
for help?

When you don't have any business with me, try to
show your face in the field as much as possible.

At first, I didn't look much different from the
other vegetables.

Lately, my language has improved quite a bit, and
I've been wandering around the fields.

Miiru-chan, you're really delicious. I'm living
for moments like this.

I see, in that case, I guess I can offer my body
as well.

Actually, this relationship is quite mutually
beneficial.

This child can eat delicious food, and somehow I
feel like my body's fatigue is being relieved...
And

...If we're both feeling good, then I suppose it's
within the acceptable range for my body to stick
to yours.

Ah... \i[249] Haa... \i[249] Miiru-chan, it feels
too good... I'm going to...

Every time you suddenly release, from now on,
please say I'm coming before doing so.

As I instructed, he faithfully declares 'I'm
coming' before releasing.

Somehow, that behavior is cute and makes me feel a
little complicated, but

I guess it can't be helped... Alright, let it out
and let's feel good together, okay?

Ah... Miiru-chan, you're too cute! I'm going to...
I'm going to...!
Nn... feels good... chu... nnn... lick...
Nn... feels good... chu... nnn... delicious...

Since I noticed that this child's secretions are
sweet and delicious

I try to lick it as much as possible, and
sometimes as a service, I let my tongue crawl on
the tentacles, and he reacts so noticeably, it's a
little cute.

Haa... \i[249] Haa... \i[249] Miiru-chan, you're
so cute \i[249]

I noticed something else besides the sweet
secretions

As we continue our acts, this child is visibly
growing before my eyes.

Even now, the words I speak have become smoother,
and I feel like the large bud that I can see right
in front of me has also grown in size.

The reason I continue these acts is not so much
simple assistance to others as it is

I'm curious about what kind of flower will bloom
when that bud opens.
What will you do today? Will you continue?

Depending on the day, there are times when I
continue this act several times, but more often
than not, it ends after one time.

Hmm... I see. Then, I'll take you up on your offer
and do it one more time--...!

Suddenly, the tentacles start to growl intensely,
and a voice of agony begins to leak out.

My whole body is burning up... If I stay like
this... it's no good.
It's coming out... It's being born...!

What do you mean by it's being born? Is that how
plants feel when they give birth!?

While I'm in confusion, this child is suffering...
What should I do!?
It's no good anymore! I... I...!

Just when I thought the area was illuminated by a
mysterious light, there...

No way! Miiru Onee-chan, that's terrible! It's me,
it's me!
Um... I... I don't have a name... hehe

Suddenly, I look over the child who appeared in
front of me from top to bottom.

I don't recognize the upper part, but the lower
part is a familiar plant... which means...

Are you the contents of the bud!? You're not a
flower at all, and there's still a bud on top of
your head!
Hehe... I love you, Miiru Onee-chan~

Could it be that a girl came out from the bud...
It's okay if it's a girl, right?
Huh? I wonder how it is...

Um, if the breasts are big or there's no
genitals... and no dick, then basically it might
be a girl?

Huh? Even though Miiru Onee-chan doesn't have any
breasts...

In that case, could it be a girl? There's a hole
in the crotch area, but it seems like there's no
dick attached.

Can you stop calling me 'that' and call me by my
name? ♪
Eh... but don't you not have a name?

That's right, isn't it? So, Miiru Onee-chan, you
decide.

No way! No way, no way! I've never decided on a
name...

I want my beloved person to decide for me... is
that not allowed...?

I guess there's no helping it... um. Then, your
name is... Light...

L-Look! It has some squiggly tentacles, and it's
kind of cute, isn't it?

Taking a letter from my name is like a bonus, it's
kind of childish, and...

If you don't like it, then it's fine to choose
another one! Just do as you please!

No... I'm so happy... I... Roel... am very happy
right now.

I see... well, thank goodness. Then, once again,
Roel, please take care of me from now on!
Yes! Please take care of me, Miiru Onee-chan!

It's become a bit strange, but if this child...
Roel is happy, then I guess it's okay...

Come to think of it, what should we do about meals
from now on? It seems to have a mouth, so should
we eat from there, or...

Enter from the next door to the tool shop. I
didn't come here to play today.
I came to buy some items, you know!
Enter through the door right next to us.
